message.content:
1. Thirty-six health facilities participated in the IDCAP trial.
2. The health facilities were randomly assigned to two groups: Arm A and Arm B.
3. Each group, Arm A and Arm B, consisted of 18 health facilities.
4. Two MLP in Arm A received IMID.
5. Two MLP in Arm B received IMID.
